*.nps
*.npt
*.psess
*.vsp
*.vspx

# --- PACKAGES ---
# Ignorar cache local de pacotes, mas manter o manifest.json
Packages/com.unity.*
!Packages/manifest.json
!Packages/packages-lock.json

# --- PROJETO ---
# Mantém as cenas, assets e scripts
Assets/
!Assets/**/*
!ProjectSettings/**/*
!Packages/**/*
